•	The -6% was a harsh acceleration, confirming a serious downturn.
•	The final -24% was a historic capitulation event. This was not just a correction; it was a market crash. The weakness of the preceding months gave the bears the freedom to unleash their full force, pushing the market to a point of maximum pessimism.
